posts.subject: Patreon Videos
posts.body:
Anyone got any of her patreon videos? I find youtube links in various forums at times but, by the time I get to them, they're taken down.
I don't even know how many there are, which shoots had videos for them. But I -do- know I'm still dying to see her latest Krampus video. Goddamn.
Can anyone help?
What's the file format? Says jpg but they won't load
Correct. It says so in each file name. But they're -not- jpgs because no program is loading them, even ms paint. What file format are they then?
Even downloaded irfanview, never used it before. Every program I use says "unsupported file format"
